    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Analyst Memo Generator\\n\",\"**NLP Project 88 of 100** — Turn raw notes into structured analyst memos.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import re, requests\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"RAW_NOTES = \\\"\\\"\\\"Call with client ABC Corp - March 2025\\n- Revenue up 18% YoY to $12M\\n- New product line launching Q3\\n- Hiring 50 engineers, expanding to Austin\\n- Concerned about supply chain delays\\n- Competitor XYZ gained 5% market share\\n- Budget for marketing increased 25%\\n- CEO optimistic about second half\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\ndef notes_to_memo(notes):\\n    lines = [l.strip('- ').strip() for l in notes.split('\\\\n') if l.strip().startswith('-')]\\n    # Categorize\\n    financials = [l for l in lines if any(w in l.lower() for w in ['revenue','budget','%','$'])]\\n    risks = [l for l in lines if any(w in l.lower() for w in ['concern','delay','risk','competitor'])]\\n    opportunities = [l for l in lines if any(w in l.lower() for w in ['launch','hiring','expand','optimistic','new'])]\\n    \\n    memo = '📋 ANALYST MEMO\\\\n' + '='*40 + '\\\\n\\\\n'\\n    memo += '💰 Financial Highlights:\\\\n'\\n    for f in financials: memo += f'  • {f}\\\\n'\\n    memo += '\\\\n⚠️ Risks & Concerns:\\\\n'\\n    for r in risks: memo += f'  • {r}\\\\n'\\n    memo += '\\\\n🚀 Opportunities:\\\\n'\\n    for o in opportunities: memo += f'  • {o}\\\\n'\\n    memo += '\\\\n📝 Recommendation: Monitor supply chain risks while capitalizing on growth trajectory.\\\\n'\\n    return memo\\n\\nprint(notes_to_memo(RAW_NOTES))\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Memo generation structures raw notes** into actionable categories.\\n\",\"- **Keyword-based categorization** separates financials, risks, and opportunities.\\n\",\"- **For production, use LLMs** for more nuanced categorization and synthesis.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
